	dprr:hasNoteText "Quaestor pro pr. Named in an inscription of Tibur, probably early Augustan: Pacceio L. f. I q. pro pr. | Ostienses | navicularei (CIL 14.3603-ILS 6171; Aepig. 1955, no. 178). See Wiseman, NM 248, no. 299.\n" .
